transcript:
Customer: Hello.
Executive: Haan.
Customer: Namaskar, Abhishek baat kar raha hu IndiaMART se main aapka.
Executive: Haan boliye sir.
Executive: Haanji, sir, ek confirm request kar raha tha na lead se related.
Customer: Haan, haan, haan.
Executive: Haanji, maine aapko kal bhi call karne ki koshish kari thi aap shayad busy the.
Customer: Haan, wo sir driving kar raha tha na kal isliye.
Executive: Haanji, haanji, to matlab kya issue aa raha hai lead se related?
Customer: Lead se related nahi aa raha hai apne ko, apne ko abhi order nahi mil rahe hai ye baat hai. Leads vagera to apne kar rahe hai.
Customer: Free sale to quotation bhi dal rahe hai usme.
Customer: Inquiry bhi dal rahe hai, sari tarah se apne dalte hai, follow up bhi le rahe hai.
Customer: Har jagah ka.
Customer: Variation bhi apply kar rahe hai, GST hai business hai, amount hai is type se.
Customer: Ye mere khayal se lagta hai abhi account hai na under under performer hai, upar nahi aa raha hai mere khayal se.
Executive: Aapki aapka wo kya bolte hai profile aapki listing mein.
Customer: Haan, haan.
Executive: Nahi aapki listing to matlab MBC walo ne to ki thi ji aapki listing kyuki agar aapka catalog updated hai na, aapka catalog hai matlab lagbhag hai ki main dekhu aapke catalog to main bhi first time lagata hu.
Customer: Rehta hai aapko maine pehle bhi to bataya tha ye low score wale products apne delete karna hai.
Customer: Low score wale usko to apne chalo bahut nahi hai wo lekin jo jyadatar hai barabar usme se to koi na koi inquiry apne ko aani chahiye na. Matlab inquiry bhi aati hai lekin fake inquiry aati hai.
Customer: Uska follow up le rahe hai apne, call kar rahe hai.
Customer: To bol phone utha ke bol rahe hai ki na humko jarurat hi nahi hai.
Customer: Tab inquiry ki aagyu.
Executive: Accha, matlab jab leads vagera aap uthate ho contact karte ho bahar se.
Customer: Haan, contact hai, wo sab dekhte ho kya matlab kitne mang rahe hai quantity vagera ka.
Executive: Haan, haan, haan, sara.
Customer: Ek ek do do piece bhi apne to haan to wo bhi apne sample ke taur par apne wo bhi dene ready hai lekin customer utha ke seedha hi bol de wo barabar.
Customer: Ke bhai nahi chahiye humko.
Customer: To aage koi baat hi apne kaise kar sakte hai wo phone cut kar dalte hai na phone.
Executive: Accha, ye mere khayal se editing nahi kiya hai jisne ye pura catalog banaya hai na.
Customer: Company ka pura information, description vagera jo bolte hai na.
Customer: Manufacturing ka aap logo ne unko sara photo vagera diya tha lekin unhone sahi tarike se lagta hai manage kiya nahi hai.
Executive: Aapki team ne.
Customer: Photo vagera to sab dali kyuki maine kyuki kyuki maine jis do do teen bande ka ya hum baat ka profile dekha tha na unka matlab pura factory unit ka matlab description achcha hasta likha hua tha design vagera achcha kiya hua tha.
Customer: Design bhi kafi badhiya kiya hua tha matlab jo photo hai na usko decoration achcha kiya tha unhone.
Customer: Apna kuch aisa hai nahi jo maine photo diya usko hi waha pe unhone chipka diya hai.
Executive: Nahi photo to jo aapne di hai wohi dali hui hai isme kyuki photos to dali hui hai.
Executive: Abhi jaise ye aapka low spot small gemstone tree ho gaya iski aapne ek hi photo di hai iski to ek hi dali hui hai shayad aapne kitni photo di thi?
Customer: Maine photo to unko matlab jo manufacturing unit ki hai office ki hai wo sari photo di thi lekin jo matlab decorative product banane ka hota hai na unhone wo banaya nahi hai.
Customer: Aisa hoga to main aapko photo bhejunga.
Customer: Dusre jo log hai na unka account kis tarah se decorative matlab pura setup itna achcha se kiya hai na waisa apna hai nahi abhi main meri side se kholta hu mera profile.
Customer: To matlab unke comparison mein to sara kafi low hai.
Executive: Profile wise, accha dusro ka kholte ho.
Customer: Haan, profile profile profile thik se nahi banayi.
Executive: To profile matlab dusro ka kis tarah khola tha aapne matlab MBC chala raha tha wo bhi hai ya kuch aur chala raha tha.
Executive: Matlab samjha nahi service kabhi matter matlab service kabhi matter karta hai na sir agar wo higher service chala raha hoga to uski profile alag hi dikhegi kyuki uske usme verification dikhega aur uska jo matlab wo hoga aapka jo website usko milti hai jaise aapko bhi milti hai to website jo milegi wo website uski alag dikhegi.
Executive: Company ka logo nahi aapne dal rakha hai company ka logo usme dal rakha hoga aapne company ka logo provide karaya tha?
Customer: Karaya tha na unko diya hi tha maine pura detail diya hua tha.
Executive: Accha.
Customer: Wahi to baat kar raha hu main maine manufacturing ka diya tha office ka diya tha logo diya tha.
Customer: Sara detail wise unko diya tha.
Customer: Company mein kitne log kam karte hai us hisab se pura detail usko diya hua tha.
Executive: Accha, aap ek kam karo abhi matlab aap free ho to matlab ek kam karte hai aapko screen dikhaunga aapko apne google meet pe aap mujhe batana ki kya nahi dala.
Customer: Abhi to main ek order hai uska main bajar pe nikla hu saman kharidne matlab pura abhi ek order chalu hai uska main hamara export ka kam hai na to uska bhi main wo vagera kam karne nikla hu main aapko free padta hu to aapko whatsapp par hi karke message karunga fir aapko screen share karta hu.
Executive: Haan ya to aaj agar aap din bhar mein kabhi bhi free raho matlab.
Customer: Haan wahi wahi time pe do 2 baje baad main free rahunga 2 baje baad bhi aapko main message karunga.
Executive: Theek hai aapka lunch time baad.
Customer: Lunch time baad aapko main 2 baje baad bhi main free hu ghar pe office mein hounga pura din dopahar baad.
Executive: Haan 2 baje baad.
Executive: Haan theek hai.
Customer: Haan.
Executive: Theek hai.

None
